snippet.title: (SM64 Mod) SM64 Shining Stars Repainted RELEASE
snippet.description:
The full release to SM64 Shining Stars Repainted! Travel back to the areas from SM64 Shining Stars a few months after the events of Shining Stars 3!
Enjoy!

Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nUPmRBKBGeDcZFpbc3YIl_Ay-jzjsZ3G/view?usp=sharing

Music:
Rayman 3 - Once Upon a Time: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SgW5SbzznP4
Kirby Returns to Dreamland - Looming Darkness (remix by scarps): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ePLGu5iB48M
_________________________________________________________________
All other projects (as zip): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hhzAV5AvTIAqATafAt3tLtZmlqKaSDLb/view
